Package: cd2030
Title: Data Loading, Validation, and Reporting for Countdown 2030
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: cd2030 is a comprehensive R package designed to streamline
    data management and validation for Countdown 2030 initiatives. It
    efficiently handles data formatted according to the Countdown 2030
    standardized structure, providing functionalities for data loading,
    cleaning, and validation. The package automatically identifies and
    addresses common data quality issues, ensuring data adherence to
    Countdown 2030 guidelines. It performs comprehensive checks, including
    completeness, consistency, outlier detection, and ratio consistency,
    to guarantee data integrity. cd2030 generates standardized reports
    summarizing data quality and identifying potential issues, saving
    researchers time and effort and enabling them to focus on data
    analysis and interpretation.
